Customer: Hello

Executive: Achcha achcha achcha to stone temple ki lead nahi hai na to tender mein aapko dikha raha hai.
Customer: Hamesha yahi dikhata hai.
Executive: Haan nahi lead hogi tab to wahi dikhayega agar lead hogi stone temple ki present time mein tab to fir lead dikha dega aapko otherwise wo tender aapko show kar raha hai.
Customer: Search kholta hu tab yahi rehta hai isme.
Executive: Achcha achcha.
Executive: Abhi jo lead mujhe dikh rahi hai India pe recent karne ke baad galaxy stone panel ki hai red sand stone ki hai. Grey pio stone panel stone wall panel sand stone wall panel aise kar ke show kar rahi hai. Stone temple ki present time mein lead nahi hai to aapko tender dikha raha hai tender se ko main dekh leta hu supply of outdoor indoor fountain supply of one set of roof or drain set achcha supply of outdoor indoor fountain achcha.
Executive: Present time mein nahi hai sir lead maine dekh liya stone temple dal ke bhi iski wajah se nahi show kar raha hai to fir wo tender ka section open kar deta hai aapke liye kyuki waha pe match making aap jo search kar rahe ho na waha dikh jata hai is wajah se.
Customer: Baaki unse to main sir connect mein hu aapne number diya tha na.
Executive: Hm hm.
Customer: To unko guide to kiya hai kafi abhi jo hai lead manager use bhi kar rahe hain reply reply bhi badhaya hai to uska farak aapko jo hai jaldi hi dekhne ko milega sir.
Customer: Aur ye photo achcha theek hai ye to photo aapne yaha bhi bhej di thi whatsapp pe theek hai koi dikkat nahi hai.
Executive: Ek sir call aayi thi buyer ki receive nahi kiya aapne kuch pata hai us call ka?
Customer: Kab aayi thi?
Executive: Bata raha hu main aapko aaj 30 tarikh hai theek hai sir kal aayi thi sham mein 7:30 baje.
Customer: 7:30 baje ho sakta hai phone charge mein laga diya us time aayi hua. Sir number bhejo na mere ko main baat kar leta hu.
Executive: Sir number aapke lead manager mein aa gaya hoga mujhe dikhaata nahi hai na sir number wo number hai main batata hu mujhe pura dikhata nahi hai lekin main fir bhi batata hu 63 se start hai aur last mein 907 hai.
Customer: 63
Executive: 63 se start hai aur last mein 907 hai mujhe beech ka number nahi dikhata hai sir.
Customer: 908
Executive: 77 last mein 907.
Customer: 907 chalo main dhundta hu.
Executive: Haan isko dhund lijiyega aap.
Executive: Hai na baaki sir catalog mein score aapke badhane ke liye kaise kaise karwaun jo sir ka jo number diya hai inko unke paas photo to available hogi.
Customer: Hm hm.
Executive: Hai kyuki photo ka kya hai na sir kuch kuch thoda sa score down ho raha hai photo ki wajah se wo pixel sizes nahi rehte hain samajh rahe hain aap ya keh sakte ho 200 product hai aapke 113 113 product sorry hai na 33 product to badhiya hai bilkul 36 product aise hain jiska score medioker 50 60 aa raha hai aur 41 ka to kafi jyada low hai.
Customer: Ye to low hai karan kya hai iska?
Executive: Haan karan main aapko bata deta hu ek minute dekho main aapke product section mein gaya aur short by lagata hu store low to high ab dekho sir ek product jaise design is designer stone pillar naam hai sir theek hai ab isme minimum teen photos lagni hai product ki.
Customer: Hm hm.
Executive: To uske us us jo aapne ek photo lagai bhi hai wo chhoti hai theek hai to teen photo aise lagni hai jiske sizes bhi badhiya ho aur product photo bhi achchi ho to score milega ja kar ke aapko aur fir fir specifications ka hai chalo wo to main add kar dunga to koi problem nahi hogi wo to sahi ho jayega aapka wo to maine kar bhi diya hai fir aapko karna hai ki teen photo lagani hai to 85 ka aapko jo hai score yaha pe mil jayega abhi 45 hai aise hi kuch kuch products hai polished stone fountain yellow stone wall panel hai na stone cladding building ye chakkar hai usme teen teen photos lagni hai sir ek bar unko bol dijiye jo sir chalate hain na laptop desktop unko bol dijiye ek bar ki har har product mein do do same product ki do teen photo aur add karte hain.
Executive: Tab sir jo hai aapki visibility bhi achchi hai.
Customer: Aisa aisa nahi ho sakta hai kya jinka kaise is isko low aa raha hai unko hata hi do bilkul hi khatam kar do.
Executive: Are sir hata doge to fir business kaise kaise aayega matlab product to aap hi ke hai na sir product dikhega jitna dikhega tab tab to bikne ke chances badhenge aapke aisa kuch problem nahi hai wo to add kar sakte ho photos hoti bhi hongi aapke paas even aap bahut sare clients ko bhejte bhi hoge main ek bar dekhta hu aapke profile mein ya lead manager se try karta hu agar photo milti hai to main add karta hu badhata hu isko aapka bhi.
Customer: Photo to bahut sari hai pillar ki range ki photo to main aur bhej dunga.
Executive: Koi baat nahi main ek bar dekhta hu khud se karta hu mujhe jo kam padta hai fir main ek ek photo aapse mang lunga haan to sahi rahega kyuki ek sath mangunga to fir main bhi nahi samajh paunga kaun sa product kis mein lagega kaun si photo kis mein lagegi to pehle main aapke lead manager se dekhta hu jo satik baithta jayega add karta jaunga aur jo nahi baithta jayega wo aapse mangunga theek hai main abhi karwata hu aaj isko ekdam priority ka aaj sunday hai lekin fir bhi main karwaunga aapka kam theek hai.
Customer: Theek hai sir.
Executive: Theek hai sir karata hu mangta hu fir aapse.
Customer: Haan jo bhi zarurat pade to mere ko bata dena main bhej dunga aapko.
Executive: Haan sure sure.
